## 04. KEY LEARNINGS THIS SESSION (additive to existing learnings list)

- Claude's Higgsfield MCP toolset has no video object-removal/inpainting tool — only generate / upscale / reframe / outpaint / background-removal. Higgsfield's own **web app** has a separate feature, **Kling 3.0 Omni Edit** ("Kling O1 Video Edit" in some UI states), for prompt-based video editing including element removal and local repaint. Bill accesses this directly in-browser; Claude cannot call it via MCP.
